{"tid":1183880,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇試過成功係街問男/女仔叫咩名同拎電話","createTime":"2019-06-03T09:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T09:37:42.000Z","uid":45831,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9c98776f153bcea191d07efe1e6d7e3bf792f81d","tid":1183880,"uid":45831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:17:00.000Z","msg":"有冇成功真係做到朋友/情侶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咁多未知數下都去問 其實好勇敢<br />\n<br />\n有次個男仔直程踩住架單車係我隔離問我有冇男朋友 我笑住話有就走左<br />\n過多排又撞到佢 佢又踩住架單車黎問我有冇男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好攪笑<br />\n<br />\n但最後都係吹左兩句水就走左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a584a80fecc4997d40233e33f6afbcd46eefb7e4","tid":1183880,"uid":45831,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:21:13.000Z","msg":"仲有好而以前係學校讀書 成日撞到一個男仔 好陽光<br />\n成日係圖書館偷偷望佢 <br />\n會數住星期幾 幾點 第幾次見到佢<br />\n搭到同一部𨋢就勁開心<br />\n<br />\n但最後都冇問佢攞電話 過多一排就冇再見到佢<br />\n後悔左一段時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a368e233e9011e438fa0e289911140eae042f6f2","tid":1183880,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:28:21.000Z","msg":"鬼王"},{"pid":"732f517b8cd7d806b4b662a34cd10d7f2d707312","tid":1183880,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:32:33.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"bd321f4d875a35717944be9b28405576c243b219","tid":1183880,"uid":154127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:34:49.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"f6c7e60f3d74fd353fb8ff4ae2bfeea7d7e97e95","tid":1183880,"uid":216726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:37:42.000Z","msg":"有，三個+"}]}